OL,3,CChildren's hospices risk being 'hugely
OL,4,Creduced' due to funding and cost issues
OL,6,FChildren's hospice services are at
OL,7,Frisk of being "hugely reduced" amid a
OL,8,Flack of long-term sustainable funding
OL,9,Fand rising costs, a charity has warned.
OL,11,FTogether for Short Lives urged the
OL,12,Fnext prime minister to "end the
OL,13,Fsticking plaster approach to funding
OL,14,Fthese crucial services" ahead of
OL,15,FJuly's General Election.
