OL,3,CChildren's hospices risk being 'hugely
OL,4,Creduced' due to funding and cost issues
OL,6,FThe organisation's new report, Short
OL,7,FLives Can't Wait: Children's Hospice
OL,8,FFunding in 2024, found costs at
OL,9,Fchildren's hospices are "rising
OL,10,Frapidly", with charitable expenditure
OL,11,Fin 2023/24 up by 12% to #4.5 million
OL,12,Fcompared to the previous 12 months.
OL,14,FSome 66.7% of children's hospices said
OL,15,Fthis was due to a hike in energy
OL,16,Fbills, while 86.1% said it was due to
OL,17,Fhigher costs associated with
OL,18,Frecruiting and retaining staff.
