OL,3,CChildren's hospices risk being 'hugely
OL,4,Creduced' due to funding and cost issues
OL,6,FAccording to the report, some 54% of
OL,7,Fchildren's hospices in the UK ended
OL,8,Fthe 2023/24 financial year in a net
OL,9,Fdeficit.
OL,11,FTogether for Short Lives extrapolated
OL,12,Fthe figure across all 39 hospice
OL,13,Forganisations to estimate a total
OL,14,Fshortfall of #8.5 million.
OL,16,FIn the current financial year, 72% of
OL,17,Fchildren's hospices are forecasting a
OL,18,Fnet deficit, the report added, with
OL,19,Fthe total estimated to top #30 million.
