OL,3,CChildren's hospices risk being 'hugely
OL,4,Creduced' due to funding and cost issues
OL,6,FTogether for Short Lives also made a
OL,7,FFreedom of Information (FOI) request
OL,8,Fto integrated care boards (ICBs),
OL,9,Fwhich 40 out of 42 responded to.
OL,11,FBased on the information shared, the
OL,12,Fcharity estimated ICBs spent an
OL,13,Faverage of #145.16 for every case of
OL,14,Flife-limiting conditions in patients
OL,15,Faged zero to 24 in their local area, a
OL,16,Ffall of 5% compared to the previous 12
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,19,FIt also revealed ICB funding varied by
OL,20,Fas much as #366 per child in 2023/24.
