OL,3,CChildren's hospices risk being 'hugely
OL,4,Creduced' due to funding and cost issues
OL,6,FAndy Fletcher, chief executive of
OL,7,FTogether for Short Lives, said
OL,8,Fchildren's hospices "are at a turning
OL,9,Fpoint" ahead of the General Election.
OL,11,F"Our report paints a bleak picture of
OL,12,Frising costs, local funding cuts and
OL,13,Fthe prospect of lifeline services for
OL,14,Fseriously ill children being hugely
OL,15,Freduced unless the next government
OL,16,Fintervenes urgently," he added.
