OL,6,FTogether for Short Lives is calling on
OL,7,Fthe next government to review how
OL,8,Fchildren's hospice care is funded and
OL,9,Fcommit to maintaining, ringfencing and
OL,10,Fincreased the #25 million in NHS
OL,11,FEngland funding for services by the
OL,12,Frate of inflation.
OL,14,FThe charity also said it wants ICBs
OL,15,Fheld to "greater account" for the way
OL,16,Fin which they commission children's
OL,17,Fpalliative care.
