OL,6,FMr Fletcher added: "For 18 years,
OL,7,Ffamilies have relied on the central
OL,8,FNHS funding for children's hospices.
OL,9,FThe parties must commit to continuing
OL,10,Fit for the long term as a #25 million
OL,11,Fringfenced grant which increases with
OL,12,Fthe rate of inflation."
