OL,6,FCorey, 14, was diagnosed with cerebral
OL,7,Fpalsy at 18 months and is now
OL,8,Freceiving palliative care. The family
OL,9,Fhas been supported by Claire House
OL,10,FChildren's Hospice since 2016.
OL,12,FMr Watkins said: "They don't just help
OL,13,Fthe boys, they help our two other
OL,14,Fchildren and us as a family. The
OL,15,Fsibling events are brilliant. They
OL,16,Falso put things on for us, so I play
OL,17,Fgolf with the dads and meet other
OL,18,Fparents that have disabled children.
